## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Basic understanding of cybersecurity concepts
- Virtualization software (VMware, VirtualBox, or equivalent)
- Kali Linux or similar penetration testing distribution
- Python 3.x for security scripting labs

### Quick Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/assessment-labs.git
cd assessment-labs
./setup-environment.sh  # Initializes lab environments
